<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>73</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams, Tune: &quot;Pilgrim's Farewell&quot;</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki ma Pi̱ki ma!
 Pi̱ki ʋba binili ma!
 Chiso ilbʋsha pia hʋt
 Himak nitak fehna hoka,
 E chim anumpohonla chi̱,
 Ish pim aiahni pulla cha,
 Auet ish pi apelashke.
.    
     Chi Shilombish okʋt
.    
     Pim a̱ya pulla cha,
.    
     Pi chu̱kʋsh mominchit
.    
     Pi nuktalalashke.
 Pi̱ki ma! Pi̱ki ma!
 Pi̱ki ʋba Chihowa ma!

[V2]
 Chisʋs ma! Chisʋs ma!
 Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
 Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke.
 Hatak ilbʋsha pia ha̱
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo pulla cha
 Chim anukfila hanta ka
 Et ish pihi̱ma pullashke
.    
     Pi Okchalinchi ma!
.    
     Chi anukchietot,
.    
     E chim asilhha ka,
.    
     Et ish pi haklashke.
 Chisʋs ma! Chisʋs ma!
 Chisʋs ʋba pi̱ Mi̱ko ma!</lyrics>
<time_sig>(6.8.8.8.8.8.8.) with Refrain (6.6.6.6.) 6.8.</time_sig>
<title>Pi̱ki ma Pi̱ki ma! ƲIT73</title>
</song>